description:
Spacious studio in a very quiet and safe neighborhood. Just three blocks to the 7 train, which will get you to Grand Central in just 15 minutes or to Times Square in 20!  One block away from a brand new grocery store and two blocks to a 24 hour CVS. Amazing restaurants serving all types of cuisines within walking distance. Great place to rest up before you head out and explore the city!

A great little reprieve from your daily adventures in the city.

The whole studio is yours for your stay!

I will not be here during your stay, but you can reach me by phone if there is an emergency.

This is a very safe, family oriented neighborhood. It is very quiet at night.

3 blocks from the 7 train, which will get you to Grand Central in 15 minutes or Times Square in 20.
